My Kitchen Rules Australia Series 5 Episode 15

My Kitchen Rules Australia is back for 2014

Manu Feildel and Pete Evans return to host and judge the ultimate home-cooking battle!

Gate crashers Josh and Danielle take their turn in the kitchen as the competition heads back to Victoria. With an interest in molecular gastronomy, will the experimental foodies confidence match their menu?
